data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. DON'T MISS THIS OPPORTUNITY! GREAT HOME IN A GREAT LOCATION! Three bedroom home with office that can easily be converted to a fourth bedroom! Natural lighting galore in this open floor plan that is great for entertaining! A great one story plan spanning over 2,100 square feet of living on an oversized home site. When approaching the home you are greeted by a gorgeous front yard with beautiful mature landscaping as well as a welcoming huge front porch where you can spend mornings, afternoons or evenings. This home offers new HVAC System installed end of 2021, high ceilings, detailed arches, columns, niches and much more. From the front door when you walk in you look straight through to the great room and then outside through the screened lanai to the large fully fenced backyard! This home has a spectacular design! When you enter the back patio you are greeted by a large backyard yet secluded, private oasis with beautiful landscaping and tons of yard space to do anything your heart desires! You can sit out back to take in nature and beauty as the rolling hills of Minneola give you room for a beautiful distant scenery with just the occasional sounds of birds chirping. It truly is the best of both worlds! This home is nestled in the beautiful neighborhood of Highland Oaks which has just now approved the addition of a play ground for the community! Come visit this beautiful home in this warm, friendly neighborhood because you are sure to want to stay forever! Zoned for the brand new Aurelia Cole Academy K-8! Located just moments from access to the Florida Turnpike, the new Publix Shopping Plaza, CVS and much more! Located just moments from the future Minneola Town Center which will have all kinds of retail shopping, restaurants and much more. You are just a couple of moments from the rolling hills of Clermont, Lakeridge Winery and Southlake Hospital as well. Convenient to all of this yet tucked away in a rural setting! Roof is original but is in good condition and free of leaks as it has been inspected by a local licensed roofing contractor and they have confirmed that roof is in good and insurable condition. Current insurance quote available upon request. Seller's preferred lender is giving a free 1% rate buy down for one year, waived lender fees and no closing costs re-finance! Seller has an assumable mortgage. Sellers rate is currently 2.99%.
